title: Commission Regulation (EEC) No 1760/89 of 20 June 1989 amending Annex II to Council Regulation (EEC) No 4134/86 concerning certain textile products originating in Taiwan
header:
COMMISSION  REGULATION (EEC) No 1760/89
of 20 June 1989
amending Annex II to Council Regulation (EEC) No 4134/86 concerning certain textile products originating in Taiwan
THE COMMISSION OF THE EUROPEAN COMMUNITIES
main_body: Annex II to Regulation (EEC) No 4134/86 is hereby amended in accordance with the Annex hereto.

This Regulation shall enter into force on the day following its publication in the Official Journal of the European Communities.
It shall apply with effect from 1 January 1989.
This Regulation shall be binding in its entirety and directly applicable in all Member States.
attachments:
Done at Brussels, 20 June 1989.
For the Commission
Frans ANDRIESSEN
Vice-President
(1) OJ No L 386, 31. 12. 1986, p. 1.
(2) OJ No L 293, 27. 10. 1988, p. 58.
(3) OJ No L 124, 8. 6. 1970, p. 1.
